surement period (X), a ratio for their values can be obtained and used to indicate a possibility, wherein the possibility could be the presence of radioactive material associated with the volume of material; or the absence of radioactive material associated with the volume of material; or uncertainty as to whether there is radioactive material associated with the volume of material; or the presence of high atomic number material associated with the volume of material.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>